Title: Battle Pet Tamers: Outland
Description:
You've bested the master tamers of Kalimdor and the Eastern Kingdoms, but your next challenge will be far more trying.

There are four tamers in Outland that you must now defeat: Nicki Tinytech in Hellfire Peninsula, Ras'an in Zangarmarsh, Narrok in Nagrand, and Morulu the Elder in Shattrath.

You must defeat them to proceed on the path to greatness.
ObjectivesText: Defeat Nicki Tinytech, Ras'an, Narrok, and Morulu the Elder in pet battles.
PortraitTurnInText: Another step in your journey, complete.
